description: Nidorina are a larger and stronger form that female Nidoran take when they gain enough experience. In the main Pokémon game series, a Nidorina can be found as wild Pokémon in the Kanto and Johto regions of the Pokémon world, and it can also be acquired when a female Nidoran grows past experience level 16 and is evolved into a Nidorina.
name: Nidorina
